\s Mwokozi wangu ulikwenda juu
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Mwokozi\bd*\bd  wangu ulikwenda juu kukaa kuumeni kwake Baba; Utakusanya sisi sote huko, \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd  kwako, utatufikishsa. :/: Makao mema wa’tuandalia, unatungoja kwake Mungu Baba. :/: \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Mwombezi wetu wewe, \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  Kristo\bd*\bd , kwa’jili yetu mbele yake Baba. Wachunga sana sisi, kundi lako, na watusaidia ’jaribuni. :/: Na siku zote unatuombea, watushindia vita kali huku. :/: \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Mikono yako uliwanyoshea walio wako, siku uli’kwenda; na hivyo siku utakaporudi utabariki wakuaminio. :/: Ulivyokwenda, utakavyorudi; niombe nikakeshe kwa imani!. :/: \bd*
